Package eu.etaxonomy.cdm.model.description

Provides classes: to describe specimens, observations or taxa, to associate other factual informations to specimens, observations or taxa (including distribution), to support identification by means of keys.

Package eu.etaxonomy.cdm.model.description Description

Provides classes:

  • to describe specimens, observations or taxa,
  • to associate other factual informations to specimens, observations or taxa (including distribution),
  • to support identification by means of keys.
